204032.desc: Thank you for inviting me on this wonderful trip. Now that I have donned this beautiful outfit, shall we partake of a Sakura Empire tea party– leisurely and elegantly?
204032.name: Porcelain Grace

203080.desc: York-class heavy cruiser - Exeter, Hull Number 68!
203080.name: Exeter

206033.desc: Ah, big brother, you're here... Ehehe, I only just got here as well. Um... shall we go then? I kind of... want to go to the amusement park...
206033.name: Long-Awaited Date

204033.desc: Beauty is not always over the rainbow. Sometimes it is right in your backyard. Commander, how would you like to spend this quiet, lovely day right here with me?
204033.name: Dawnlight's Dame

202271.desc: My, what brings you here, Commander? Are you feeling unwell? That's no good... Why don't you come sit over here first? I'll start by taking your temperature...
202271.name: Pure White Angel

203049.desc: Whew... At long last, after all that hard work, I get to wear this uniform as well. Even though all I did was... Huh? Lead by example? Be a role model? I don't get it...
203049.name: Suffolk (Retrofit)

206034.desc: So this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire... Changing into it is difficult but... if you like it, then Unicorn is happy!
206034.name: Prayer of Plum and Snow

205050.desc: King George V-class battleship – King George V.
205050.name: King George V

202272.desc: Commander, I've brought the chair. If you don't want to get in the water, feel free to sit here. ...Hm, me? Of course, I will remain by your side.
202272.name: Pure White Holiday

203050.desc: Norfolk-class heavy cruiser - Norfolk, Hull Number 78!
203050.name: Norfolk

206019.desc: Our glory coalesces into the bonds that forge a bright new future! Let's rev it up! Hermes, retrofit complete!
206019.name: Hermes (Retrofit)

206035.desc: So I'm... an "idol" now... I'm not sure how well I'll do... But I'll give it my all...!
206035.name: Angelic Night

203019.desc: Um... Your Excellency, could you please stop staring at me like you don't recognise me? I didn't think that I'd get a new look for my retrofit, either... But, don't you think it's rather cute?
203019.name: London (Retrofit)

202273.desc: Would you care for some afternoon tea, Commander? Heehee~ This is one of my little hobbies when I'm not performing my maid duties.
202273.name: Graceful Afternoon Tea

205020.desc: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Warspite, Hull Number 03!
205020.name: Warspite

203020.desc: London-class heavy cruiser – Shropshire, Hull Number 73!
203020.name: Shropshire

205021.desc: This year, I am in charge of delivering presents to the children of the Royal Navy. Let's get going once I finish decorating this Christmas tree!
205021.name: Christmas Warrior

202291.desc: Aurora chose this outfit for me because... the Spring Festival represents a time of celebration in the Dragon Empery, and red is the color that best symbolizes that. What do you think? Does this outfit... make you feel more festive?
202291.name: Ruby-Red Boudoir

205101.desc: Hehe~ As this medical facility training is crucially important, a charismatic leader such as myself would be best suited to instruct everyone on– Wait a moment, what's with this outfit?! You there, explain the meaning of this at once!
205101.name: Mischievous Little Nurse

205022.desc: We have the finest equipment. Now to turn in a performance worthy of Her Majesty's beauty... Behold, the Royal Stage!
205022.name: Under Pleasure

204038.desc: If the smooth path only allows one person to travel at a time, then I’ll gladly walk the path not taken with you hand-in-hand.
204038.name: Rosey Love Poem

205070.desc: King George V-class battleship - HMS Duke of York.
205070.name: Duke of York

203070.desc: York-class heavy cruiser - York, Hull Number 90!
203070.name: York

203071.desc: The school has recently been consumed by a series of Mysteries... there must be some Mastermind lurking behind the scenes. Yes, another Tribulation awaits me! I shall part the veil and reveal all Truths!
203071.name: Truth Seeker

203040.desc: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Suffolk, Hull Number 55!
203040.name: Suffolk

203072.desc: O Unfathomable King of the slumbering depths, hear the call of my Force and step into this world through the Azur Gate! ...Huh, Commander? Why did you show up?
203072.name: Summoner from the Azure Depths

205041.desc: Although it's a gift from the Commander, it's still embarrassing to wear this....Commander, do you think you could teach me how to swim?
205041.name: Future Seaside Admiral

205073.desc: My beautiful Adonis, why dost thou refuseth to take refuge in the trove of everlasting love... Perhaps my outfit can finally pierce thy heart? Hehe~
205073.name: Prestige of the Glorious Formula

203089.desc: Commander, what do you think? I look more mature than I did before... right?
203089.name: Exeter (Retrofit)

205010.desc: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Queen Elizabeth, Hull Number 00!
205010.name: Queen Elizabeth

203010.desc: London-class heavy cruiser – London, Hull Number 69!
203010.name: London

202280.desc: I am the light cruiser, Dido, currently taking part in idol activities as part of the experimental Muse System. I learned more or less what idols are supposed to do from the others, so p-please... keep a close eye on me!
202280.name: Dido µ

205090.desc: King George V-class battleship – Howe (HMS Howe.)
205090.name: Howe

203090.desc: London-class heavy cruiser, Sussex. Hull Number 96.
203090.name: Sussex

205011.desc: Hah haah! You're a lucky servant this evening! We shall allow you to accompany us to the party! ... B-but it's not like I chose you because I like you! I just... Yes! I just sort of chose randomly! Got it?!
205011.name: The Queen's Ball

205091.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, but now I'm ready to– Commander? What's the matter? It'll get dark soon if you keep standing around like that.
205091.name: Noble Rouge

203091.desc: What are you spacing out for? Have you not gotten tired of staring at all the swimsuits yet? Good grief... Are you able to help set up the parasol or the beach chairs at least?
203091.name: Sunlit Tulips

205012.desc: Now this is a stage worthy of our majesty! You are not to leave our sight, servant! Let your passions burn for me!
205012.name: One Night of the Queen

205060.desc: King George V-class battleship – Prince of Wales, Hull Number 53!
205060.name: Prince of Wales

203060.desc:
Norfolk-class heavy cruiser, Dorsetshire, Hull Number 40
<color=#fad545>Unlock build after receiving</color>
203060.name: Dorsetshire

203092.desc: What are you staring at me for? I'm just the same as any of the others... Y-you have a few more hands to shake? Of course...
203092.name: Wine and Red Roses

205013.desc: Hehe, behold the new outfit that I had Akashi make for me! Impressive, no? Prostrate yourself before the elegant charm of my school uniform, servant~♪
205013.name: Queen of the Campus

205029.desc: Warspite, retrofitting complete. Mm, I rather like this feeling of being rejuvenated... Now, Commander, let us make our way towards new battlegrounds!
205029.name: Warspite (Retrofit)

205061.desc: I'm not a big fan of beach volleyball, but Hood begged me... I swear, that girl! She just can't get enough of the sun! You've got to cheer for me!
205061.name: Sun Shining Upon Windsor

205014.desc: Did I hear that you're supposed to give out red envelopes during the Dragon Empery's New Year? This is a fine chance to display the magnanimity of the Queen of the Royal Navy! ...Don't just run off with your gift! Spread the word of my glory, my servant!
205014.name: Crown Jewel of the Royal Navy

203030.desc: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Kent, Hull Number 54!
203030.name: Kent

206038.desc: This is... an important outfit for an important ceremony... yes! Unicorn and Yuni are both ready for this! Big brother... how do I look?
206038.name: A Dream of Pure Vows

206036.desc: Oh, big brother... Unicorn is reading right now. Mm, yeah, while eating ice cream... Big brother, want to have a bite?
206036.name: Icy-Sweet Storytime

205062.desc: I've been wearing Royal attire my whole life, so a change in pace doesn't seem bad. Oh, Commander, good timing. Can you explain to me how to celebrate the New Year here?
205062.name: Sakura Elegance

206030.desc: Aircraft carrier – Unicorn, Hull Number I72!
206030.name: Unicorn

206031.desc: Unicorn... is now a songstress... *giggles* Unicorn's song has reached Onii-chan's heart.
206031.name: Little Star Songstress

205031.desc: This is such a weird costume… oh well, it’s Halloween after all. It cannot be so bad, this is a fun activity after all. First things first, I didn’t say that I would join from the very beginning!
205031.name: Luna Witch

204031.desc: What a feast for sore eyes. I feel great~! Vacations really should be at the beach! Let's show Sara your beach ball, Cygnet!
204031.name: Lady of the Shining Sun

206010.desc: Hermes-class aircraft carrier – Hermes, Hull Number 95!
206010.name: Hermes

205102.desc: Why the astonished look on your face? You heard me correctly! On this day, I am not merely Valiant, I am the regal and royal Queen Valiant!
205102.name: Queen Valiant I

205072.desc: Ahh, this luscious scent... comes from thee. What dost thee feel when gazing upon my new dress? Hehe... your lips may lie but your eyes do not...
205072.name: Eternal Night's Carola

203079.desc: This is no mere Upgrade, this is an Awakening! I will alter the course of fate itself!
203079.name: York (Retrofit)

205064.desc: Oh, Commander. Worry not. Since I've been given this job, I will see through it until the end. Besides, it's been a while since I've gotten this fired up. Haha!
205064.name: The Laureate's Victory Lap

206032.desc: This... present... is for you... I hope you like it... What? Me wearing this outfit is the best gift I can give you? Co... Commander!...
206032.name: The Gift of Spring

205051.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander... I don't get to wear a dress very often, so it took me a bit longer. Let's get going, then. Remember, you'll be the lead tonight. Haha~
205051.name: Rose's Regalia

205048.desc: I never imagined that this dreamlike situation would come to pass... Commander, have you also been looking forward to sharing this moment with me? Hehe~
205048.name: Palace of Blessings
